description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 48, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 96, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, Nine Lives for South, and 5 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80482-94954-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [96 Votes, Common]
